# n8n-workflow-all-templates Project Rules

## Overview

This project is a collection of 7400+ n8n workflow JSON templates with a Next.js explorer (Browse + Templates) and Python scraper. See [n8n-project.mdc](mdc:n8n-project.mdc) for full project details.

